OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FThousands of struggling households
OL,7,Fcould benefit from a new relief scheme
OL,8,Faimed at writing off up to #500
OL,9,Fmillion of household energy bill debt.
OL,11,FEnergy regulator Ofgem says plans will
OL,12,F"reset and reform" Britain's energy
OL,13,Farrears, which have heaped additional
OL,14,Fpressure on all household bills.
OL,16,FCurrently, every UK household pays an
OL,17,Fextra #52 a year through their energy
OL,18,Fbill, under the current price cap, to
OL,19,Fcover energy bills that are never paid
OL,20,Fand have to be written off.
