OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FOfgem said it expects to write off up
OL,7,Fto #500 million of historic debt,
OL,8,Fbuilt up during the recent energy
OL,9,Fcrisis, in a move which could help
OL,10,Faround 195,000 people.
OL,12,FThe regulator confirmed that a final
OL,13,Fconsultation on the first phase of its
OL,14,Fdebt relief scheme is set to be
OL,15,Fpublished shortly.
