OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FFigures published by Ofgem last month
OL,7,Fshowed that the money owed to
OL,8,Fsuppliers by households in England,
OL,9,FScotland and Wales surged to a new
OL,10,Frecord high of #4.4 billion by the end
OL,11,Fof June.
OL,13,FThe average debt for people who do not
OL,14,Fhave a repayment plan with their
OL,15,Fprovider currently stands at about
OL,16,F#1,716 per household.
