OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FOfgem said that in a worst case
OL,7,Fscenario, between #1.1 billion and
OL,8,F#1.7 billion of historic debt,
OL,9,Faccording to supplier estimates, is
OL,10,Fnever paid and will be written off.
OL,12,FIt comes only a day after MPs called
OL,13,Fon the regulator to pay down some of
OL,14,Fthe energy debt bill through windfall
OL,15,Fprofits on suppliers.
OL,17,FHowever, the cost of unpaid debts will
OL,18,Fcontinue to be covered by being
OL,19,Freclaimed across all households' bills.
