OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FOfgem said it is pushing forward with
OL,7,Fproposals to bring the debt down and
OL,8,Freform how these debts are managed in
OL,9,Forder to prevent it growing as high in
OL,10,Ffuture and therefore reducing the cost
OL,11,Fto all households.
OL,13,FOther proposals by Ofgem include plans
OL,14,Fto trial changes to the process
OL,15,Fhouseholds must follow when they move
OL,16,Finto a new property.
