OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,FCharlotte Friel, director for retail
OL,7,Fpricing and systems at Ofgem, said:
OL,8,F"We know the growing amount of debt in
OL,9,Fthe energy system is a significant
OL,10,Fchallenge.
OL,12,F"We must protect consumers by striking
OL,13,Fthe right balance between making sure
OL,14,Fthose that can pay are supported to do
OL,15,Fso, and targeting support at those who
OL,16,Fneed it most.
