OL,3,COfgem to write off #500m of energy
OL,4,Cdebt in major relief plan
OL,6,F"These proposals will both directly
OL,7,Freach households and relieve the
OL,8,Fburden of unmanageable debt, while
OL,9,Falso making changes to the way that
OL,10,Fdebt is managed in the sector."
OL,12,FThe first phase of the scheme, set to
OL,13,Flaunch early next year, will focus on
OL,14,Fpeople in receipt of means-tested
OL,15,Fbenefits with more than #100 of debt
OL,16,Fbuilt up during the energy crisis.
